If you play sounds, either using play() or loop(), they won't pause playing when the application is minimized (on Windows) or paused (on Android). Music doesn't have the same problem.
To reproduce you can use the following minimal example:

```
public class MyGame extends Game {
    @Override
    public void create() {
        Sound s = Gdx.audio.newSound(Gdx.files.internal("mySoundEffect.ogg"));
        s.loop();
    }
}
```

